{
  "stem": "17299.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We tried to get out of Germany, and we could not have any business anymore because all Jewish businesses were closed.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was forced to work for a farmer, and we would get minimum wage.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then I had to-- a short time later, I had to work on the Autobahn, which was very difficult.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I had to go to Dusseldorf by train, and I had to work there six days a week.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By train.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My oldest brother, he got a phony paper that he could go to South America.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He got released on the concentration camp, and he had to do forced labor in a swamp nearby.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The Germans were drying out a swamp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so was my youngest brother.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We could go home every day, but we had to do a certain amount of work every day for minimum wage.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there was also a special tax for Jews because they were not-- not member of the Army, and there was an extra 15% tax taken off the salary for that purpose.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We had no problem with that till the war started.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then it was more difficult to get everything.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But since we were still self-sufficient with most of the things, we had no problems there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, we remained in our own house.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were disregarded and [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] in general, we in the town had no problem, but in the cities there were problems.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Jews were assaulted on the street and things like that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, but we got also a visa to go to Chile.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we made the booking and everything, but the war broke out.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We could not get out of Germany anymore.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "First it was in Dusseldorf.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
